I'll do it.

600
00:44:08,570 --> 00:44:10,504
Count me in.

601
00:44:24,353 --> 00:44:26,514
Don't you listen to him.

602
00:44:26,555 --> 00:44:29,353
Nobody is ever gonna put
any of our horses down.

603
00:44:29,390 --> 00:44:32,121
You understand?
Don't you worry.

604
00:44:34,863 --> 00:44:37,093
